IUCN Categories 2

points
dark theme
Simple IUCN categories mapping.
Author

D. de Vienne

Published

November 25, 2025

Show the code 
import polars as pl
from pylifemap import Lifemap

# Load iucn dataset
iucn = pl.read_parquet(
    "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Lifemap-ToL/pylifemap/main/data/iucn.parquet"
)

Lifemap(iucn, width="100%").layer_points(fill="status").show()
Warning: 862 taxids have not been found in Lifemap database.
